node.text:
CHICKEN PARM MAC AND CHEESE

INGREDIENTS
2 chicken breasts
150g plain flour
1 tsp dried Italian seasoning
2 eggs, whisked
140g panko breadcrumbs 
30g grated parmesan cheese
Oil for shallow frying
 
30g butter
30g flour
500ml milk
½ tsp mustard powder
¼ tsp paprika
? ? tsp nutmeg
Salt and pepper to taste
400g cooked macaroni
100g grated mozzarella,
100g grated cheddar
50g grated gruyere
 
250g tomato pasta sauce 
50g grated mozzarella cheese
Fresh basil leaves

node.title: Your Favourite Chicken Parm Recipe EVER! FACT! 😍🤤🐓

node.text:
CHICKEN PARM SPAGHETTI PIE

INGREDIENTS
* 	2 chicken breasts, butterflied
* 	Salt & pepper, to season
* 	100g flour
* 	4 eggs, beaten
* 	180g panko breadcrumbs
* 	1 ltr vegetable oil, for frying
* 	800g spaghetti
* 	150g parmesan
* 	5 eggs
* 	250ml double cream
* 	1 tbsp salt
* 	1/2 tbsp black pepper
* 	Sliced mozzarella
* 	1 tablespoon olive oil
* 	1 large onion chopped
* 	2 teaspoons minced garlic
* 	400g tomato passata
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
* 	1 teaspoon dried Italian herbs
* 	1 teaspoon sugar

2 tbsp flour
Salt and pepper
1 lb diced stewing beef

1 tbsp butter
2 onions, diced small
500g mushrooms, sliced
2 cloves garlic, diced small
2 tbsp flour
1 tbsp tomato paste
2 cups red wine
1 1/2 cups beef stock
1 tsp salt
1 tsp pepper
 
Calzone Dough:
½ cup warm water
.25oz dry yeast
1 tsp yeast
½ cup water
2 tbsp olive oil
2 tbsp honey
¼ tsp salt
3 cups plain flour
 
Grated Cheddar Cheese
 
Garlic Butter:
½ cup salted butter
3 cloves garlic, minced
1 tbsp Chopped parsley
Pepper

CHICKEN PARM MAC AND CHEESE

INGREDIENTS
2 chicken breasts
150g plain flour
1 tsp dried Italian seasoning
2 eggs, whisked
140g panko breadcrumbs 
30g grated parmesan cheese
Oil for shallow frying
 
30g butter
30g flour
500ml milk
½ tsp mustard powder
¼ tsp paprika
? ? tsp nutmeg
Salt and pepper to taste
400g cooked macaroni
100g grated mozzarella,
100g grated cheddar
50g grated gruyere
 
250g tomato pasta sauce 
50g grated mozzarella cheese
Fresh basil leaves

node.text:
It’s dinner time! Try this Lasagna Stuffed Meatloaf log - you won’t regret it!

INGREDIENTS
1lb beef mince
2/3 cup breadcrumbs
2 eggs, whisked
1/4 cup finely chopped parsley
3 coves garlic, minced
1 tbsp tomato paste
1 tsp salt
1 tsp pepper
2 cups ricotta
1 tsp salt
1/2 tsp pepper
4 Fresh Lasagna noodles cut to bundt size
1 1/2 cups tomato sauce
Mozzarella slices
•

•

CHICKEN PARM SPAGHETTI PIE

INGREDIENTS
* 	2 chicken breasts, butterflied
* 	Salt & pepper, to season
* 	100g flour
* 	4 eggs, beaten
* 	180g panko breadcrumbs
* 	1 ltr vegetable oil, for frying
* 	800g spaghetti
* 	150g parmesan
* 	5 eggs
* 	250ml double cream
* 	1 tbsp salt
* 	1/2 tbsp black pepper
* 	Sliced mozzarella
* 	1 tablespoon olive oil
* 	1 large onion chopped
* 	2 teaspoons minced garlic
* 	400g tomato passata
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
* 	1 teaspoon dried Italian herbs
* 	1 teaspoon sugar
